fulltitle: Playing it UNsafe Composer Journeys: Henry Threadgill Part 1
description: Henry Threadgill discusses his piece 'No Gates, No White Trenches, Butterfly Effect', which is being written for American Composers Orchestra as part of the 2010/11 'Playing it UNsafe' series. 'No Gates, No White Trenches, Butterfly Effect'  will receive its world premiere performance at Zankel Hall, Carnegie Hall in NYC on March 4, 2011.
